PROTO-Proposal DB9  (Vanyel)
Randomness
(Creates a rule)

All occurrences of the word "random" or forms of it shall be taken to
mean "any of the choices with equally distributed possibility for
each".

***End Proto

That should take care of a few ambiguities.

Vanyel


