 Proposal
 Randomness
 (Creates a rule)
 
 All occurrences of the word "random" or forms of it shall be taken to
 mean "any one of the choices with equally distributed possibility for
 each".
 
 ***End Proposal

NOTE: This was protoed.  (As were each of the others which I proposed
this week.)
 
